FWIW---it REALLY helps the conference folks if you pre-reigister. They're not
freaking daily as to whether they can meet expenses. It also speeds things up
considerably at the registration table. It helps scheduling and space
concerns and EVERYTHING! I know it's VERY close, but if you haven't already,
I'm sure Holly would appreciate it!

Kelly
